    <item>
      <title>Configure VCF Operations Collector Groups</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/post/operations/vcf-91-configure-sso-openldap/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/post/operations/vcf-91-configure-sso-openldap/</guid>
      <description>
        
          
            &lt;h2 id=&#34;configure-vcf-operations-collector-groups&#34;&gt;Configure VCF Operations Collector Groups&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create a collector group and assign VCF Operations collectors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VCF Operations APIs Used&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;POST /suite-api/api/auth/token/acquire&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;POST /suite-api/api/collectorgroups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;GET /suite-api/api/collectorgroups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-a-collector-group-using-curl&#34;&gt;Create a Collector Group using Curl&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Procedure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Connect to the VCF Operations Fleet Management appliance over SSH.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Replace the values in the sample code with values for your VCF Operations instance and run the commands SSH session.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;vcfOpsFqdn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;$&amp;#39;flt-ops01a.rainpole.io&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;vcfOpsUser&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;$&amp;#39;admin&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;vcfOpsPass&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;$&amp;#39;VMw@re1!VMw@re1!&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;collectorPrimary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;$&amp;#39;10.11.10.38&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;collectorSecondary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;$&amp;#39;10.11.10.39&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;collectorGroupName&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;$&amp;#39;sfo-collector-group&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;collectorGroupDescription&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;$&amp;#34;San Francisco - Collector Group&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start=&#34;3&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Authenticate to VCF Operations and obtain a token by running the following command:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;TOKEN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;curl -k -X POST https://&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$vcfOpsFqdn&lt;/span&gt;/suite-api/api/auth/token/acquire -H &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;Content-Type:application/json&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; -d &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;{&amp;#34;username&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$vcfOpsUser&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;password&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$vcfOpsPass&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;authSource&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;LOCAL&amp;#34; }&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; jq -r &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;.token&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start=&#34;4&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Obtain the IDs of the Collectors by running the following commands:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;collectorPrimaryId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;curl -k -X GET &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$vcfOpsFqdn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;/suite-api/api/collectors&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Authorization: vRealizeOpsToken &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$TOKEN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Accept: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Content-Type: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; jq &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;.collector[] | select(.hostName == &amp;#34;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$collectorPrimary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#34;) | .id&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;collectorSecondaryId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;curl -k -X GET &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$vcfOpsFqdn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;/suite-api/api/collectors&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Authorization: vRealizeOpsToken &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$TOKEN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Accept: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Content-Type: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; jq &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;.collector[] | select(.hostName == &amp;#34;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$collectorSecondary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#34;) | .id&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start=&#34;5&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create a new collector group and assign the collectors by running the following command:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;collectorGroupId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;curl -k -X POST &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$vcfOpsFqdn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;/suite-api/api/collectorgroups&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Authorization: vRealizeOpsToken &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$TOKEN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Accept: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Content-Type: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -d &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;{&amp;#34;systemDefined&amp;#34;: false, &amp;#34;haEnabled&amp;#34;: false, &amp;#34;lbEnabled&amp;#34;: false, &amp;#34;name&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$collectorGroupName&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;collectorId&amp;#34; : [ &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$collectorPrimaryId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$collectorSecondaryId&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39; ], &amp;#34;description&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;si&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;collectorGroupDescription&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;si&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#34;}&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; jq -r &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;.id&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start=&#34;6&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Verify the collector group has been created by running the following command:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;curl -k -X GET https://&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$vcfOpsFqdn&lt;/span&gt;/suite-api/api/collectorgroups -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Authorization: vRealizeOpsToken &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$TOKEN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Accept: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -H &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Content-Type: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; jq &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;.collectorGroups[] | select(.name == &amp;#34;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$collectorGroupName&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#34;)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-a-collector-group-using-powercli&#34;&gt;Create a Collector Group using PowerCLI&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Procedure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
          
          
        
      </description>
